Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,180)\fs20\4a&HFF&\fn华文行楷\3c&H18C2E7&\1c&H000000&\3a&HD2&}武士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,180)\fs20\4a&HFF&\fn华文行楷\3c&H18C2E7&\1c&H000000&\3a&HD2&}魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就选这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹰学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  你这装扮太劲爆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选了枪手就变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长你的也很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在菜单中选装备的话可以查看自己的样子
